# Privacy Policy

Last Updated: July 2026

Thank you for using VibEats.

Your privacy is important to us. VibEats has been designed with privacy in mind and collects only the information necessary to provide its features.

## Information We Collect

Depending on how you use VibEats, we may collect:

- Your approximate or precise location (only after permission is granted)
- Restaurant ratings
- Reviews you choose to create
- Photos you choose to upload
- Favorite restaurants
- Saved collections
- Search history
- App preferences

## Location

Location is used to:

- Find restaurants nearby
- Improve restaurant search
- Display your current area

Location is only accessed after you grant permission.

You may revoke location access at any time in your device settings.

## Photos

If you choose to attach photos to your reviews, VibEats will request access to your photo library.

Photos are never uploaded without your action.

## Data Storage

Some information may be stored locally on your device, including:

- Favorites
- Ratings
- Search history
- Preferences

Future versions of VibEats may offer cloud synchronization.

## Analytics

VibEats may collect anonymous usage information to improve the application.

This information does not include your restaurant reviews or personal messages.

## Third-Party Services

VibEats uses Apple technologies including:

- Apple Maps
- Core Location

Future versions may integrate with additional services.

## Sharing

If you choose to share a review on Instagram, Facebook, or another service, the information you choose to share will be handled according to that platform's privacy policy.

VibEats does not automatically publish content on your behalf.

## Children's Privacy

VibEats is not directed toward children under the age of 13.

We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

## Your Choices

You may:

- Delete your ratings
- Delete saved restaurants
- Clear search history
- Revoke location permission
- Remove photo permissions

